description:
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Are you passionate about patient care? We are looking for qualified nurses to join our bank. We want nursing staff that are enthusiastic, committed and prepared to go that extra mile for our patients.&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;We are currently recruiting dedicated and motivated individuals across a variety of disciplines to join the Staff Bank at North Devon District Hospital based in Barnstaple.&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Do you want?:&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;• To be an integral member of a dedicated team working within your local hospital?&lt;br /&gt; • To join a forward thinking and innovative organisation, which puts their patients first?&lt;br /&gt; • To contribute to the provision of high quality care within your local community?&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;If you do, then we want to hear from you.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;We can offer flexible working and an attractive salary.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;If you are currently employed by the Trust and want to join the Northern Healthcare Trust Staff Bank then please contact the recruitment team at ndht.staffbank@nhs.net as you do not need to apply for this vacancy.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Previous applicants need not apply.&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Interviews will be completed via Zoom or telephone during the current climate.&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
